        "haller-led-34": {
          "description": {
            "text": "Easy climbing leads to a ledge beneath a striking, elegant, slightly overhanging wide crack. One, or preferably two, Camalot #5/Friend #5s and one Camalot #4/Friend #4 are required. Tops out on a ledge with fixed nuts forming an abseil anchor.",
